Petapa Agung, gunakan skill penilaian.

62
00:04:09,100 --> 00:04:09,970
Jawaban.

63
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:13,560
Ramuan ini setara dengan ramuan penuh.

64
00:04:14,350 --> 00:04:17,650
