94
00:06:02,340 --> 00:06:03,420
Biarkan aku lewat.

95
00:06:08,590 --> 00:06:10,300
Rigurd, kamu tidak apa-apa?

96
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:12,390
Tu-Tuan Rimuru!

97
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:12,930
Eh?

98
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:16,310
