101
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:26,740
Betul.

102
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:28,450
Oh, Rimuru!

103
00:06:28,450 --> 00:06:29,070
Duh.

104
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:34,490
Karena dia meremehkan kita, jadi aku memberinya pelajaran!

105
00:06:36,410 --> 00:06:39,330
Aku adalah salah satu dari Tiga Musketir Raja Iblis Carrion.

106
00:06:39,330 --> 00:06:41,210
Taring Macan Tutul Hitam, Phobio.

107
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:44,670
Prajurit terkuat di antara prajurit monster Raja Monster.

108
00:06:45,090 --> 00:06:46,760
Kota ini lumayan juga.

109
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:50,800
Cocok untuk dikuasai oleh Raja Monster. Kamu juga berpikiran sama, 'kan?

110
00:06:51,010 --> 00:06:52,050
Jangan bercan—

111
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,900
Raja Iblis Milim?

112
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,990
Pukulan Api Taring Macan Tutul!

113
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:15,990
