206
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,000
Ketua—

207
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,960
Shh.

208
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:03,010
Duh, gawat!

209
00:13:03,010 --> 00:13:03,840
Tapi, tapi ....

210
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:06,430
Hei, kalian ... hati-hati, dong!

211
00:13:06,890 --> 00:13:10,180
Bagaimana bisa kalian bertahan hidup padahal selalu gegabah begini?

212
00:13:10,970 --> 00:13:13,600
Kelihatannya ada kelompok yang sedang berhadapan dengan monster.

213
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,480
Ketua, kita harus bagaimana?

214
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:21,070
Hei! Tunggu, dong!

215
00:13:22,690 --> 00:13:23,990
Permisi!

216
00:13:23,990 --> 00:13:25,150
Terima kasih bantuannya!

217
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:26,530
Maaf, ya!

218
00:13:26,530 --> 00:13:27,490
Dia datang!

219
00:13:31,330 --> 00:13:32,620
Knight Spider?!

220
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,290
Kalian semua, siapkan formasi.

221
00:13:36,250 --> 00:13:38,170
Kalau ada yang terluka, segera sembuhkan.

222
00:13:38,580 --> 00:13:40,750
